data.description: Investment property for sale! Add this legally zoned duplex to your portfolio. The owner has already started the demo. Some upgrades such as plumbing and electrical has been started and now it just needs some of your touches to complete the project. The property will be delivered with all materials included on the premises. First floor host one bedroom and one full bathroom apartment. Only the first floor has a private entrance to the backyard and there is a door that leads to the basement. On the second floor you will discover two spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom as well. The first floor apartment you can easily collect a minimum of $950 or $1236 with Section 8.  Second floor you can collect a minimum of $1250 or $1476 with Section 8. Schedule your showing today! This is a great house hack or another investment property to add to your portfolio.
